<h1>Agreement</h1>
<div class="mt-5 mb-5 form-group application__group application__group--agree">
    <h5>Please read and check each rule to indicate that you understand and agree: <span class="required">*</span></h5>
</div>
<div class="terms-grid">
    <div class="application__term">
        <input type="text" id="understanding1" class="initial-input application__term-check" maxlength="2" required />
        <label for="understanding1" class="application__term-label">
            I understand that if I am approved as eligible, it may take 30â€“60 days for my service provider to
            apply the Oregon Lifeline benefit to my account.
        </label>
    </div>
    <div class="application__term ">
        <input type="text" id="understanding2" class="initial-input application__term-check" maxlength="2" required />
        <label for="understanding2" class="application__term-label">
            I give the Oregon Public Utility Commission (OPUC), the Federal Communications Commission, and the
            Universal Service Administrative Company authority to review any records needed to confirm my
            eligibility.
        </label>
    </div>
    <div class="application__term">
        <input type="text" id="understanding3" class="initial-input application__term-check" maxlength="2" required />
        <label for="understanding3" class="application__term-label">
            I understand that my household can only get one Lifeline benefit.
        </label>
    </div>
    <div class="application__term">
        <input type="text" id="understanding4" class="initial-input application__term-check" maxlength="2" required />
        <label for="understanding4" class="application__term-label">
            I understand that if I violate the one-per-household rule, I will be de-enrolled from the Oregon
            Lifeline program.
        </label>
    </div>
    <div class="application__term application__term-list">
        <div class="application__term">
            <input type="text" id="understanding5" class="initial-input application__term-check" maxlength="2"
                required />
            <label for="understanding5" class="application__term-label">
                I agree to notify the PUC within 30 days if:
            </label>
        </div>

        <ul class="application__list">

            <li class="application__item">I move.</li>
            <li class="application__item">I disconnect service.</li>
            <li class="application__item">I no longer qualify for the Oregon Lifeline benefit.</li>
            <li class="application__item">I receive more than one Oregon Lifeline benefit.</li>
            <li class="application__item">Another member of my household is also receiving the Oregon Lifeline
                benefit.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="application__term">
        <input type="text" id="understanding6" class="initial-input application__term-check" maxlength="2" required />
        <label for="understanding6" class="application__term-label">
            I understand that my Oregon Lifeline benefit may not be transferred or given to any other person.
        </label>
    </div>

    <div class="application__term">
        <input type="text" id="understanding7" class="initial-input application__term-check" maxlength="2" required />
        <label for="understanding7" class="application__term-label">
            I understand that I may be required to recertify my eligibility at any time and that failure to do so
            will stop my benefit.
        </label>
    </div>

    <div class="application__term">
        <input type="text" id="understanding8" class="initial-input application__term-check" maxlength="2" required />
        <label for="understanding8" class="application__term-label">
            I understand that providing false information to obtain this benefit is punishable by law and may
            result in fines, imprisonment, or permanent disqualification.
        </label>
    </div>
</div>

<hr />

